Class Invoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scg.domain.Invoice

  • public class Invoice
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates the attributes and behavior for creating client invoices for a given time period from time cards.

    jack

        public Invoice(ClientAccount client,
               int invoiceMonth,
               int invoiceYear,
               java.lang.String propFileName)
        Instantiates a new invoice for a given client and time period. This constructor is to facilitate testing; programmers would normally use Invoice( ClientAccount, int, int ).
        Parameters:
        client - The associated client.
        invoiceMonth - The month of the target time period.
        invoiceYear - The year of the target time period.
        propFileName - The name of the properties file for printing invoices
        See Also:
